WEBVTT

00:00:01.897 --> 00:00:04.878
TAPE TWO WITH MISTER SAMUEL SILVER.

00:00:05.863 --> 00:00:08.102
vi lang hostu geven in Brisk?

00:00:09.626 --> 00:00:10.644
a yor,

00:00:10.689 --> 00:00:11.713
knap yor.

00:00:11.972 --> 00:00:13.437
un vu hostu gevoynt?

00:00:13.437 --> 00:00:15.544
ale, di zelbe ort?

00:00:20.004 --> 00:00:21.433
In Baranovitsh?

00:00:21.118 --> 00:00:22.800
neyn, in Brisk.

00:00:24.678 --> 00:00:26.765
in Brisk hob ikh gevoynt oyf eyn ort.

00:00:27.142 --> 00:00:29.330
nakher bin ikh avekgeforn keyn

00:00:30.230 --> 00:00:31.676
keyn Baranovitsh.

00:00:32.272 --> 00:00:34.410
Baranovitsh hob ikh gearbet dortn a

00:00:35.057 --> 00:00:37.566
a STOLARZ,

00:00:39.782 --> 00:00:41.295
un dort gevoynt oykhe-.

00:00:39.866 --> 00:00:44.366
un far vos hostu geganen tsu Baranovitsh? far vos hostu gegan?

00:00:43.550 --> 00:00:45.997
vayl Baranovitsh iz a gresere shtot

00:00:45.997 --> 00:00:48.096
un s'iz dort do mer fabrikn,

00:00:48.455 --> 00:00:51.993
azoy dortn hob ikh gehat mer shansn tsu krign arbet.

00:00:52.792 --> 00:00:55.655
du host gearbet di gantse tsayt in di ershte ort?

00:00:57.905 --> 00:00:59.199
yo, kimat.

00:00:59.897 --> 00:01:03.013
ober dortn in Baranovitsh hob ikh gearbet keseyder.

00:01:03.153 --> 00:01:05.527
biz di letste minut.

00:01:05.887 --> 00:01:07.535
un di lebn hot geven

00:01:07.659 --> 00:01:08.986
gut, ober?

00:01:09.566 --> 00:01:10.862
nisht azoy gut,

00:01:10.865 --> 00:01:14.151
oyfn rusishn shteyger, gut.

00:01:15.708 --> 00:01:18.622
host gevoynt azoy vi a yidisher, ober?

00:01:18.678 --> 00:01:22.385
gevoynt in a hayzl, bay yenem in a shtibl,

00:01:22.442 --> 00:01:23.854
ikh mit di froy.

00:01:24.315 --> 00:01:25.710
un zi hot gearbet?

00:01:25.327 --> 00:01:26.941
zi hot geneyt, yo.

00:01:27.285 --> 00:01:29.625
zi hot gemakht kleyder, zeyer sheyn gemakht.

00:01:31.571 --> 00:01:32.690
ober nokh

00:01:32.690 --> 00:01:35.525
Br- Brisk du hot geganen tsu Baranovitsh?

00:01:35.098 --> 00:01:35.970
yo.

00:01:35.972 --> 00:01:37.793
un vi lang hostu geven dortn?

00:01:39.722 --> 00:01:42.858
biz me hot un undz genumen, in eyn un fertsikstn yor,

00:01:42.858 --> 00:01:44.187
hot men undz geshikt

00:01:44.295 --> 00:01:45.926
keyn Sibir.

00:01:46.303 --> 00:01:48.778
un du host gearbet a gantse tsayt dortn?

00:01:48.378 --> 00:01:49.182
yo.

00:01:48.885 --> 00:01:50.398
un vu hostu gevoynt?

00:01:50.454 --> 00:01:52.322
gevoynt dortn bay yenem,

00:01:52.918 --> 00:01:54.009
in a shtibl.

00:01:54.588 --> 00:01:57.147
s'iz geven a sakh yidishe mentshn dortn?

00:01:57.322 --> 00:01:58.801
yo, a shpor bisl.

00:01:59.060 --> 00:02:00.455
s'iz geven a shul?

00:02:01.052 --> 00:02:02.357
dos veys ikh nisht.

00:02:02.357 --> 00:02:04.539
dort hot men shoyn nisht getrakht vegn keyn shuln.

00:02:05.810 --> 00:02:06.719
s'iz geven a

00:02:06.719 --> 00:02:07.739
a harter,

00:02:07.739 --> 00:02:09.554
hart, ober shver

00:02:09.554 --> 00:02:11.542
ge- gelebn dortn?

00:02:11.767 --> 00:02:17.009
avade iz geven sh- shver, vayl undz zenen shoyn geven oyf di badingungen vi di rusn lebn.

00:02:17.538 --> 00:02:21.363
un zey veysn yedn eynem, hobn nisht keyn keyn shum luksus,

00:02:21.504 --> 00:02:24.425
az me hot tsu der zet a shtikl broyt iz geven ALRIGHT

00:02:25.098 --> 00:02:28.096
du host gehert fun da- der

00:02:28.187 --> 00:02:30.797
dayn familye, vos iz geven in Varshe?

00:02:31.140 --> 00:02:33.784
mayn fa- yo, ikh hob fargesn tsu dertseyln,

00:02:34.059 --> 00:02:35.927
zayendik in Brisk,

00:02:36.759 --> 00:02:39.420
iz mayn yingerer bruder, der MIETEK,

00:02:40.134 --> 00:02:44.477
er iz geganen tsurik keyn Varshe, er hot gevolt ariber brengen dem tatn mit di mamen,

00:02:44.522 --> 00:02:45.900
mit di mishpokhe.

00:02:46.698 --> 00:02:48.397
mayns a shvester

00:02:49.702 --> 00:02:51.856
iz geven krank oyf tifus,

00:02:53.718 --> 00:02:57.037
dos iz di yingere, di eltere tokhter iz nisht gevezn

00:02:57.667 --> 00:02:59.551
zi zol geyn, zi iz nisht

00:02:59.658 --> 00:03:01.998
gekent geyn, zi iz geven krank un dos.

00:03:03.455 --> 00:03:07.466
azoy un der mayn foter hot moyre gehat er vet darfn esn treyfes,

00:03:09.210 --> 00:03:11.685
er hot moyre gehat er vet esn treyf in in Rusland.

00:03:12.382 --> 00:03:14.925
az me hot gedankt got s'iz do a shtikl fleysh,

00:03:15.926 --> 00:03:19.526
ikh hob key- sh- keyn shtikl, ikh meyn a shtikl broyt.

00:03:19.571 --> 00:03:21.911
ver hot getrakht dortn vegn fleysh?!

00:03:22.153 --> 00:03:25.202
hot er moyre gehat un er iz nisht gegangen. mayn muter hot gevolt geyn,

00:03:25.848 --> 00:03:29.825
un der foter hot nisht gevolt geyn, iz er aleyn gekumen tsurik.

00:03:32.919 --> 00:03:35.259
du host gehert mer fun dayn,

00:03:34.370 --> 00:03:36.173
mir dakht zikh er hot gebrengt

00:03:36.173 --> 00:03:40.845
di di mumen, azoy dakht zikh, dortn tsurik.

00:03:43.145 --> 00:03:44.776
vos zogt "du host gehert"?

00:03:45.221 --> 00:03:49.015
du host gehert fun di mame un der foter?

00:03:48.714 --> 00:03:50.176
neyn, ⟨NOTHING⟩.

00:03:49.035 --> 00:03:50.177
shpeter?

00:03:50.250 --> 00:03:51.611
shoyn gornisht gehert.

00:03:51.887 --> 00:03:56.049
me hot gehert altsding vos me, vos me redt, me iz ariber fun oyer tsu oyer,

00:03:56.747 --> 00:03:58.035
ober azoy

00:03:58.035 --> 00:04:00.099
di tsaytungen iz gornisht gevezn.

00:03:59.868 --> 00:04:01.314
un nisht keyn brivn?

00:04:04.712 --> 00:04:05.702
gornisht.

00:04:06.720 --> 00:04:08.655
un vos iz geshen ven,

00:04:08.863 --> 00:04:11.898
ver hot gekumen un gezogt az du muzt geyn

00:04:11.898 --> 00:04:13.312
tsu SIBERIA?

00:04:15.512 --> 00:04:18.015
me hot, me hot undz gornisht, me hot gornisht gezogt.

00:04:18.015 --> 00:04:19.298
zenen gekumen tsu geyn,

00:04:19.157 --> 00:04:20.788
ve- ver hot gekumen?

00:04:20.557 --> 00:04:22.391
di N. K. V. D.,

00:04:24.135 --> 00:04:27.034
di N. K. V. D. dos iz a F. B. I. azoy vi do,

00:04:27.034 --> 00:04:30.305
yents heyst N. K. V. D. hot es geheysn.

00:04:31.796 --> 00:04:33.934
um tsvelef bay nakht,

00:04:34.327 --> 00:04:36.037
zenen gekumen mit SAMOCHODn,

00:04:36.037 --> 00:04:38.692
un gegebn a nem, un fertik arayn,

00:04:40.790 --> 00:04:41.966
zenen geve-

00:04:40.841 --> 00:04:42.168
un avekgeshikt.

00:04:43.305 --> 00:04:45.847
a ban, ober a TRUCK?

00:04:44.773 --> 00:04:48.024
a ban iz geshtanen shoyn dortn greyt,

00:04:48.688 --> 00:04:51.399
me hot genumen un tsugefirt tsu der ban,

00:04:52.569 --> 00:04:53.846
a sakh mentshn?

00:04:53.919 --> 00:04:54.690
yo.

00:04:54.948 --> 00:04:55.820
vifl?

00:04:56.552 --> 00:04:58.538
a ban in vifl se ken arayngeyn,

00:04:58.661 --> 00:05:00.680
hot gekent arayn,⟨fregt⟩ veys nisht, efsher UNK

00:05:01.175 --> 00:05:03.734
akht vagones, tsi nayn vagones,

00:05:04.078 --> 00:05:06.266
nor vos, s'iz nisht geven azoy fil mentshn,

00:05:07.166 --> 00:05:08.308
in Baranovitsh.

00:05:08.887 --> 00:05:12.408
geven froyen?

00:05:12.650 --> 00:05:13.505
vos?

00:05:13.342 --> 00:05:15.476
froyen avekgenumen?

00:05:14.270 --> 00:05:16.289
yo, ikh bin geforn mit mayn froy.

00:05:16.498 --> 00:05:18.366
un kinder gegangen oykhet?

00:05:18.860 --> 00:05:21.268
kinder iz dort nisht geven azoy fil.

00:05:21.999 --> 00:05:25.824
ober az me hot nisht aroysgenumen keyn pas, me hot gedarft aroysnemen a pas.

00:05:27.112 --> 00:05:29.199
do iz gelegn dos umglik,

00:05:29.643 --> 00:05:31.797
vos di yidn zenen arayngefaln,

00:05:32.428 --> 00:05:35.646
az me hot genumen a pas, bin ikh geblibn oyfn ort,

00:05:36.174 --> 00:05:39.172
geblibn oyfn ort, iz gekumen di daytshn hobn zey oysgeharget.

00:05:40.848 --> 00:05:43.984
un azoy hobn mir, m'iz geven in di ban shoyn,

00:05:43.987 --> 00:05:45.854
me hot gekent avekloyfn,

00:05:46.569 --> 00:05:48.555
s'iz geven mentshn vos UNK geyn,

00:05:48.830 --> 00:05:53.077
efsher me vet zayn dortn vet men kumen ⟨dikh⟩ rateven, do der front ken a mol zayn.

00:05:54.483 --> 00:05:56.334
dayn bruder hot gekumen mit?

00:05:57.032 --> 00:05:58.410
dem bruder,

00:05:59.124 --> 00:06:03.658
yo, im hot men genumen fun an ander ort, vayl er, mir zenen nisht geven tsuzamen.

00:06:04.220 --> 00:06:09.834
er iz geven mit yingere, dortn, khevre, nisht UNK nisht geven UNK, nisht geven keyn farmakhte,

00:06:10.278 --> 00:06:11.386
ober zey hobn

00:06:11.628 --> 00:06:13.597
getrogn azelkhe belkes,

00:06:14.379 --> 00:06:17.917
iz yener bruder, ze'mir ale briders geven bazunder,

00:06:18.598 --> 00:06:20.941
mayn bruder iz dokh geblibn dortn in

00:06:20.977 --> 00:06:23.700
in Brisk, in a kleyn UNK ikh bin nokh geforn,

00:06:23.700 --> 00:06:25.725
fun Brisk, in a kleyn ort,

00:06:25.736 --> 00:06:27.198
in a shtetl arayn,

00:06:30.883 --> 00:06:32.092
ober zayendik,

00:06:32.267 --> 00:06:35.293
tsurikkumendik fun dortn, nokh zayendik

00:06:35.321 --> 00:06:38.083
in in DZHIZAK,

00:06:39.033 --> 00:06:40.920
in in, ze'mir,

00:06:40.923 --> 00:06:44.714
geshribn, ikh hob geshribn tsu mayn, vos iz geven in Yisrael,

00:06:47.083 --> 00:06:51.161
un mayn bruder hot geshribn, beyde briders hobn geshribn, azoy

00:06:51.369 --> 00:06:54.333
me hot undz gegebn di adresn, di COMMUNICATION,

00:06:54.626 --> 00:06:57.050
nakher ho'mir zikh tsunoyfgetrofn tsurik,

00:06:59.334 --> 00:07:03.328
un vi, vos hostu gemakht in SIBERIA, host gearbet?

00:07:03.418 --> 00:07:05.373
gearbet, gehakt beymer,

00:07:05.373 --> 00:07:06.889
geshnitn beymer,

00:07:07.333 --> 00:07:10.669
un gemakht azelkhe kletser, glaykhe.

00:07:11.872 --> 00:07:13.841
un vi lang hostu geven dortn?

00:07:14.758 --> 00:07:16.980
in SIBERIA ikh bin geven fertsn monatn.

00:07:17.390 --> 00:07:18.987
fertsn oder fuftsn monatn.

00:07:19.348 --> 00:07:21.266
zey hot gegebn tsu esn?

00:07:21.828 --> 00:07:22.750
yo.

00:07:23.043 --> 00:07:24.708
s'iz geven gut, ober?

00:07:25.136 --> 00:07:27.276
dos hobn zey gegebn, trukene

00:07:27.276 --> 00:07:29.619
esn, ⟨me zol mir zogn⟩ kashe,

00:07:30.468 --> 00:07:36.099
oder rayz, oder andere, dos hot aleyn gekent kokhn, oyb host gevolt.

00:07:36.358 --> 00:07:38.563
az nisht ⟨host gekent⟩ esn fun kesl,

00:07:38.940 --> 00:07:41.094
⟨me hot dir⟩ gegebn a shisele un fertik.

00:07:41.572 --> 00:07:45.324
azoy nokh az mentshn hobn zikh genumen aheym beser,

00:07:45.369 --> 00:07:46.899
un zey hobn zikh aleyn gekokht.

00:07:47.107 --> 00:07:48.637
un vu hostu gevoynt?

00:07:49.740 --> 00:07:51.678
zey hobn gehat azelkhe

00:07:51.678 --> 00:07:53.565
hayzer, oyfgeshtelte,

00:07:53.688 --> 00:07:55.859
fun azelkhene, fun aza boym,

00:07:56.169 --> 00:07:58.053
hobn zey ibergeshnitn oyf helft,

00:07:58.852 --> 00:08:01.563
un zey hobn es tsunoyfgeshtelt,

00:08:01.687 --> 00:08:04.874
un di shpares vos iz geven, iz hobn zey genumen mit leym,

00:08:04.874 --> 00:08:05.917
arum un arum,

00:08:06.952 --> 00:08:08.313
un dos iz geven tsu voynen.

00:08:08.049 --> 00:08:09.714
vifl mentshn geven

00:08:09.804 --> 00:08:11.182
vu du host geven?

00:08:10.901 --> 00:08:12.650
in ⟨POSHOLEK⟩ dortn,

00:08:15.744 --> 00:08:17.985
ikh veys, s'iz geven finef hayzelekh,

00:08:17.988 --> 00:08:19.248
finef gasn,

00:08:19.845 --> 00:08:21.831
finef un tsvontsik hayzer.

00:08:23.270 --> 00:08:26.758
akht mol finef un, ken zayn a tsvey hundert mentshn iz geven.

00:08:27.236 --> 00:08:31.449
vos iz geven di nomen fun fun di TOWN vu du host geven?

00:08:31.910 --> 00:08:33.187
vi? di nomen?

00:08:33.125 --> 00:08:34.098
di nomen.

00:08:35.083 --> 00:08:36.208
Kronyove.

00:08:37.563 --> 00:08:39.211
SPETS POSHOLEK

00:08:39.875 --> 00:08:40.933
Kronyove.

00:08:41.040 --> 00:08:42.722
dos kenstu gedenken.

00:08:43.907 --> 00:08:44.758
un vi,

00:08:44.758 --> 00:08:46.788
fer- nokh fertsn monatn,

00:08:47.452 --> 00:08:50.163
far vos hostu ave- avekgeganen?

00:08:50.608 --> 00:08:52.729
me hot undz aroysgelozt, vayl mir,

00:08:52.818 --> 00:08:55.304
zey hobn geshafn a poylishe regirung,

00:08:55.304 --> 00:08:57.301
a komunistishe regirung.

00:08:58.539 --> 00:09:01.937
un di komunistishe regirung

00:09:01.937 --> 00:09:03.596
iz dokh geven dos zelbe vos zey,

00:09:04.698 --> 00:09:07.966
hobn zey gezogt, na dir, nem, kenst nemen yetst di mentshn dayne.

00:09:09.153 --> 00:09:11.240
un ven di milkhome hot zikh geendikt,

00:09:11.617 --> 00:09:12.573
s'iz gevezn ve-

00:09:12.798 --> 00:09:17.872
in zeks un fertsikstn yor, hot er gezogt ets kent forn aheym, er hot undz gegebn dokumentn,

00:09:18.097 --> 00:09:20.465
ober s'iz nisht geven zeks un fertsik yetst.

00:09:18.114 --> 00:09:19.003
ober,

00:09:20.460 --> 00:09:21.332
vos?

00:09:20.493 --> 00:09:24.234
nokh S- nokh SIBERIA iz es geven zeks un fertsik?

00:09:23.227 --> 00:09:26.478
neyn, SIBERIA iz geven frier, nokh SIBERIA, frier.

00:09:26.602 --> 00:09:28.199
dray un fertsikstn,

00:09:28.475 --> 00:09:31.473
fir un fertsik dos iz nokh alts gegangen on di shlakht.

00:09:32.255 --> 00:09:36.336
biz dem zeks un fertsikstn yor, finef un fertsikstn yor,

00:09:34.685 --> 00:09:35.709
ven,

00:09:36.336 --> 00:09:37.683
hot zikh geendikt di,

00:09:36.423 --> 00:09:39.792
ven hostu ge- avekgeganen fun SIBERIA?

00:09:40.035 --> 00:09:43.320
ven, s'iz geven, undz ze'mir aroysgeforn zeks un fertsikstn.

00:09:44.540 --> 00:09:45.614
SO nokh

00:09:46.059 --> 00:09:47.353
Kuronova,

00:09:47.207 --> 00:09:48.096
yo,

00:09:47.662 --> 00:09:49.175
vu hostu geganen?

00:09:49.856 --> 00:09:52.992
nokh Kuronyove iz men geforn tsurik keyn Poyln.

00:09:52.992 --> 00:09:53.985
ah neyn,

00:09:54.783 --> 00:09:58.287
ikh bin gevorn UNK, nokh Kornyove iz men gevezn,

00:10:01.517 --> 00:10:02.777
Balkhash.

00:10:04.875 --> 00:10:07.825
un mit dayn vayb?

00:10:07.828 --> 00:10:09.662
no-, nisht mit di brider?

00:10:07.862 --> 00:10:08.818
yo.

00:10:10.072 --> 00:10:12.041
neyn, mayn bruder hot geven in,

00:10:12.772 --> 00:10:14.659
ikh bin geforn nakher tsum bruder,

00:10:14.662 --> 00:10:17.069
fun Balkhash bin ikh geforn tsum bruder.

00:10:16.974 --> 00:10:20.731
un vos hostu gemakht, du host gearbet in Balkhash?

