ikh hob gearbet in vald dortn in in dos,

00:10:31.503 --> 00:10:36.239
in Kuronyove nisht, in Balkhash hob ikh gearbet alts, alts stolyer.

00:10:33.663 --> 00:10:34.653
Balkhash?

00:10:36.549 --> 00:10:39.328
undz hobn gehat dortn a, ikh hob gemakht dortn,

00:10:39.688 --> 00:10:40.948
sheyne zakhn.

00:10:41.814 --> 00:10:43.158
vos hostu gemakht?

00:10:45.138 --> 00:10:46.364
ikh hob zey gemakht

00:10:48.108 --> 00:10:52.423
di mebl

00:10:53.846 --> 00:10:56.929
vi zey hobn gedorfn hobn aza ANTITSHNe mebl,

00:10:57.474 --> 00:11:00.760
Ludvig, um fuftsntn, tsi um fertsntn,

00:11:01.895 --> 00:11:03.661
hobn zey mikh getrofn,

00:11:03.836 --> 00:11:05.315
zogt er, vest kenen makhn?

00:11:05.658 --> 00:11:06.901
zog ikh, ikh vel prubirn.

00:11:07.633 --> 00:11:08.825
un ikh hob gemakht.

00:11:09.827 --> 00:11:13.669
un nakher, far dem hob ikh nokh gemakht UNK andere arbetn.

00:11:14.113 --> 00:11:16.571
ober dortn in dem Balkhash,

00:11:17.235 --> 00:11:19.744
du host gearbet bay a groyser fabrik?

00:11:19.479 --> 00:11:20.199
yo.

00:11:20.357 --> 00:11:22.056
du gedenkst di nomen?

00:11:20.508 --> 00:11:21.532
di fabrik,

00:11:22.533 --> 00:11:23.805
nu Balkhash,

00:11:23.805 --> 00:11:24.857
hot geheysn,

00:11:25.318 --> 00:11:29.970
⟨Doz⟩, UNK,

00:11:30.178 --> 00:11:32.535
