hot zi gehat a gevelb mit dray tsimern.

00:16:25.794 --> 00:16:28.033
dortn di daytshn zenen dokh geven antlofn,

00:16:28.646 --> 00:16:31.020
azoy hobn undz gekent oyskloybn vos me vil.

00:16:31.937 --> 00:16:34.091
du host tsurikgeganen tsu WARSAW?

00:16:35.328 --> 00:16:37.263
ikh bin geforn keyn Varshe,

00:16:38.028 --> 00:16:39.761
hob ikh gezen alts ligt

