un un di rusn zenen geven, hot men zikh lebn zey oykhet arumgedreyt.

00:17:29.683 --> 00:17:32.833
ver se hot nisht gehat keyn fleysh, undz hobn gehat fleysh,

00:17:33.446 --> 00:17:35.330
vayl di rusishe froyen,

00:17:35.792 --> 00:17:38.419
di mener hobn dokh froyen gekumen tsu forn a sakh,

00:17:38.795 --> 00:17:42.741
dortn di, hobn zey gehat zeyers a gevelb,

00:17:42.741 --> 00:17:45.050
nisht eyns, nor tsvey oder dray,

00:17:45.680 --> 00:17:49.286
