00:17:51.553 --> 00:17:56.553
az tomer eyner hot zikh a bisl far- farzindikt, hot men gezogt, ikh vel dikh aroysshikn fun danet,

00:17:56.553 --> 00:17:57.538
nisht geven,

00:17:58.640 --> 00:18:00.845
nisht geven keyn gresere UNK klap.

00:18:01.391 --> 00:18:04.254
azoy mayn zun hot gehat vos tsu esn,

00:18:04.479 --> 00:18:09.756
me ken es zen oyf di fotografye oykhet, un,

00:18:10.503 --> 00:18:13.552
s'iz geven a sakh yidishe mentshn in shtot?

00:18:14.300 --> 00:18:15.526
zeyer a sakh.

00:18:16.393 --> 00:18:19.357
fun bafelkerung hot gekent zayn, ikh veys, a

00:18:20.831 --> 00:18:23.728
araynrekhendik di rusn,

00:18:23.902 --> 00:18:26.107
hot gekent zayn a fuftsik protsent.

00:18:26.973 --> 00:18:28.874
ober di yidn zenen avek fun dortn.

00:18:29.859 --> 00:18:30.900
shpeter?

