00:18:42.903 --> 00:18:47.049
UNK ikh hob gevolt, ikh hob oyfgegebn bites mir zoln aroysgebn,

00:18:48.000 --> 00:18:49.749
a PERMIT tsu forn,

00:18:52.404 --> 00:18:53.928
hobn zey gezogt,

00:18:53.928 --> 00:18:56.060
me hot enk derleydikt, zogt er,

00:18:56.133 --> 00:18:57.421
me hot undz opgezogt

00:18:57.421 --> 00:18:58.406
un fertik.

00:18:58.479 --> 00:19:00.274
zey hobn nisht gevolt gebn aroystsuforn,

00:19:00.285 --> 00:19:02.777
nokh tsen yor hobn zey yetst gegebn aroystsuforn.

00:19:03.491 --> 00:19:06.095
ven s'iz gekumen eyner, a minister,

00:19:06.095 --> 00:19:07.687
nisht keyn minister, nor a

00:19:07.760 --> 00:19:09.020
PRIME minister,

00:19:10.190 --> 00:19:13.307
hot er ongehoybn aroystsugebn peser,

00:19:14.240 --> 00:19:17.002
hobn ale gezogt, er iz an antisemit.

00:19:17.885 --> 00:19:19.094
zog ikh, er

00:19:19.826 --> 00:19:22.200
er iz undz dos bester fraynt.

00:19:22.526 --> 00:19:24.714
az tomer vet men nisht aroysyogn, zog ikh,

00:19:25.344 --> 00:19:26.666
veln kumen andere me vet

00:19:26.666 --> 00:19:28.427
me vet undz vayter tun shlogn.

00:19:29.327 --> 00:19:31.313
azoy az me iz aroysgeforn un fertik.

00:19:32.702 --> 00:19:35.734
ven hostu avekgeforn fun

00:19:36.431 --> 00:19:37.708
fun LEGNICA?

00:19:39.266 --> 00:19:40.729
fun LEGNICA,

00:19:41.898 --> 00:19:44.609
bin ikh geforn nokh tsvey yor, geven in WROCLAW,

00:19:46.691 --> 00:19:48.322
tsvey yor un nokh dem,

00:19:48.311 --> 00:19:50.735
far vos WROCLAW, far vos do?

