00:20:49.483 --> 00:20:51.978
un fertik. geforn dort geven dray yor,

00:20:51.978 --> 00:20:54.860
in Yisroel, hot vayter mayn bruder geshribn do,

00:20:55.743 --> 00:20:58.522
