ven hostu gekumen tsu Yisroel?

00:21:16.398 --> 00:21:17.996
zibn un fuftsikstn.

00:21:19.149 --> 00:21:21.033
un geven bizn zekhtsikstn.

00:21:21.056 --> 00:21:23.075
un vu hostu gevoynt dortn?

